---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
		title="FAQ"
		description="Frequently asked questions about Recipes Without Ads - printing, measurements, and more."
>
	<div class="page-content">
		<div class="container-narrow">
			<h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

			<div class="faq-list">

				<div class="faq-item">
					<h2>Why don't you have ads?</h2>
					<p>
						Because we don't need them! This site is simple, static, and costs very
						little to run. We'd rather provide a great experience than monetize through
						intrusive advertising.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="faq-item">
					<h2>Can I adjust serving sizes?</h2>
					<p>
						Currently, recipes show the original serving size. To adjust, you'll need to
						calculate the proportions manually. We may add an automatic scaling feature
						in the future!
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="faq-item">
					<h2>Do you have metric measurements?</h2>
					<p>
						Most recipes use imperial measurements (cups, tablespoons, etc.). For metric
						conversions, we recommend using an online converter. Common conversions:
					</p>
					<ul>
						<li>1 cup = 240ml</li>
						<li>1 tablespoon = 15ml</li>
						<li>1 teaspoon = 5ml</li>
						<li>1 pound = 454g</li>
						<li>350°F = 175°C</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="faq-item">
					<h2>Do you track my data?</h2>
					<p>
						No. We don't use any analytics, tracking pixels, cookies, or third-party
						scripts. See our <a href="/privacy/">privacy policy</a> for more details.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="faq-item">
					<h2>Can I suggest improvements to the site?</h2>
					<p>
						Maybe someday.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .page-content {
        padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
    }

    .page-content h1 {
        margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    }

    .faq-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: var(--space-2xl);
    }

    .faq-item {
        padding-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    }

    .faq-item:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
    }

    .faq-item h2 {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }

    .faq-item p {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: var(--color-text-light);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }

    .faq-item p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .faq-item ul {
        margin-left: var(--space-xl);
        margin-top: var(--space-md);
    }

    .faq-item li {
        margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
        color: var(--color-text-light);
        font-size: 1.125rem;
    }
</style>
